    public enum DateTimeStyle
extends java.lang.Enum<DateTimeStyle>
    DateTimeStyle Defined style for parsing date into string used by DateTimeUtils.formatWithStyle(Date, DateTimeStyle) and also DateTimeUtils.getTimeAgo(Context, Date, DateTimeStyle)
